com.ardock.moodapp.moodock.lib.data.persistence.utils

Interface IConvertible

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PersistentObject

    public interface IConvertible
    The IConvertible interface must be implemented by every convertible class.

    All persistent objects implement either directly or indirectly this interface.
